description.full: This game was classified by the community with the following category scores - Violence=1/3, Sex=0/3, Mature Content=0/3. Game featuring 8 levels, variety of enemies, and power ups to choose from. Take in command of the Jet to shoot in outer space and beating the final boss. Reach your goal towards a high score and getting to the top 10 list.
